videos.description: Keita Bates-Diop comes up with the defensive stop which leads to a foul on the other end.
videos.headline: Bates-Diop shows off defensive skills with a block

videos.description: Keita Bates-Diop is doing it all for Ohio State after knocking down two 3-pointers.
videos.headline: Bates-Diop hits a pair of 3-pointers for Buckeyes

videos.description: Kam Williams makes a great cut and finishes on the other side of the hoop with the right hand.
videos.headline: Williams goes back door and finishes with the reverse

videos.description: Indiana's Justin Smith trails in transition to finish the Josh Newkirk missed layup.
videos.headline: Smith cleans up miss with a monster slam

videos.description: Aljami Durham gets an and-1 opportunity as Indiana hangs with Ohio State late in the first half.
videos.headline: Durham makes circus shot as the Hoosiers cut down the lead

videos.description: Josh Newkirk puts on a great move to step into the lane and get an easy bucket for the Hoosiers.
videos.headline: Newkirk wows to get into the lane for the score

videos.description: Robert Johnson gets crafty and makes a sweet move against the Buckeyes.
videos.headline: Johnson goes behind-the-back to get a bucket

videos.description: Justin Smith tells Kaleb Wesson to smile as Smith puts Wesson on a poster.
videos.headline: IU's Smith puts Wesson on a poster with a huge baseline slam

videos.description: Kam Williams knocks down the deep jumper as Ohio State takes the lead in overtime.
videos.headline: Williams puts Buckeyes ahead in OT

videos.description: Juwan Morgan rocks the rim as the Hoosiers try and steal one at home against the Buckeyes in double overtime.
videos.headline: Morgan brings down the house with the two-handed slam in 2OT
